HEADWORD: Diversified
<hw>Di*ver"si*fied</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Distinguished
by various forms, or by a variety of aspects or objects; variegated;
<as>as, <ex>diversified</ex> scenery or landscape</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Diversifier</ent>⟦br⟧
